This is Nora that
you're talking about.

14:49.840 --> 14:53.000
It was many years
ago, after the war,

14:53.120 --> 14:55.080
with a member of
the Maori battalion

14:55.200 --> 14:59.560
who stayed on afterwards,and who went on to join

14:59.680 --> 15:01.240
the Belfast Constabulary.

