Half Maori, and half cop.

15:09.880 --> 15:10.640
[chuckling]

15:10.760 --> 15:12.240
Bugger me days.

15:12.360 --> 15:13.480
Mammy got it on with a plodder.

15:13.600 --> 15:15.160
It's not bloody
funny, all right?

15:15.280 --> 15:18.120
