15:18.240 --> 15:19.400
Bloody mammy!

15:19.520 --> 15:20.720
Poor Phineas.

15:20.840 --> 15:21.640
I need to find him.

15:21.760 --> 15:23.280
No, Carol, Carol.

15:23.400 --> 15:26.480
The lads can do that.

15:26.600 --> 15:28.480
Can we?

15:28.600 --> 15:29.960
Yes, you can.

15:30.080 --> 15:32.400
By following the trailof destruction, presumably.

15:32.520 --> 15:34.320
Then we can all
meet back at our place

15:34.440 --> 15:35.920
and watch the royal wedding.

15:36.040 --> 15:37.160
Do we have to?

15:37.280 --> 15:39.320
Yes, for Carol.

15:39.440 --> 15:42.640
Right, guess we'll
make a night of it.

15:42.760 --> 15:43.520
Come on, lads.

15:47.760 --> 15:50.240
You are such an
amazing friend.

15:50.360 --> 15:51.760
It's nothing.

15:51.880 --> 15:54.000
Go get your stuff.

15:54.120 --> 15:57.480
Well, it was all
rather special.

15:57.600 --> 15:58.920
Enjoy the wedding, ladies.

15:59.040 --> 16:01.480
I'm sure it'll be anight to remember, asshole.

16:04.600 --> 16:07.000
[music playing]

16:09.120 --> 16:10.000
No sign of him.

16:10.120 --> 16:11.000
I think that's a clue.

16:11.120 --> 16:12.240
What is?

