her, you know?

22:59.640 --> 23:00.760
Against her will.

23:00.880 --> 23:01.920
I wouldn't put it past a cop.

23:02.040 --> 23:03.280
Come on, mate.

23:03.400 --> 23:04.720
No one could force your
mammy to do anything.

23:04.840 --> 23:06.200
She wasn't a big woman.

23:06.320 --> 23:07.840
And if she'd been
on the Guinness.

23:07.960 --> 23:11.160
Ah, that's real bloody
insulting, that is.

23:11.280 --> 23:12.400
So you wanna be a
Maori because we're

23:12.520 --> 23:14.640
losers, violent, and rapists.

