I'm not saying
nothing about you.

23:16.680 --> 23:19.160
Hey, no one saying anythingbad about anyone, all right?

23:19.280 --> 23:21.240
So let's all just calm the fuckdown and have another drink.

23:21.360 --> 23:22.160
You stupid racist.

23:22.280 --> 23:23.240
Don't call me stupid!

23:23.360 --> 23:24.160
[shouting]

23:24.280 --> 23:25.080
