23:34.000 --> 23:35.160
Here.

23:35.280 --> 23:38.000
get that down you.

23:38.120 --> 23:39.680
He's usually so
happy-go-lucky.

23:39.800 --> 23:43.720
Which, you know, is anothergood thing about Maoris.

