NEWSCASTER [ON PHONE]:
What a proud father Earl

23:45.400 --> 23:46.640
Spencer must be on this day.

23:49.720 --> 23:50.600
Rita.

23:50.720 --> 23:51.960
Shh, they're about to do it.

23:52.080 --> 23:53.400
BERT: Can I use the phone?

23:53.520 --> 23:55.120
It's a toll call, but Ican transfer the charges.

23:55.240 --> 23:56.280
Shut up!

23:56.400 --> 23:57.640
Sure, maybe use
the one in the hall.

23:57.760 --> 23:58.560
BERT: Thank you.

24:07.960 --> 24:09.320
MAN [ON PHONE]: Hello.

24:09.440 --> 24:11.640
Hey, is Riana there, please?

24:11.760 --> 24:13.920
