24:14.040 --> 24:16.160
MAN [ON PHONE]:
Yeah, I'll get her.

24:16.280 --> 24:17.800
RIANA [ON PHONE]: Hi, Hone.

24:17.920 --> 24:19.520
Kia ora.

24:19.640 --> 24:21.840
I hope I said that OK.

24:21.960 --> 24:23.960
RIANA [ON PHONE]: Yeah.

24:24.080 --> 24:26.360
How was the South
African embassy?

24:26.480 --> 24:28.120
RIANA [ON PHONE]:
We never got there.

