Do you know what happened?

24:29.360 --> 24:30.520
No.

24:30.640 --> 24:32.480
We went and rallied
outside parliament,

24:32.600 --> 24:36.720
and Dave and I were meetingsome friends at the front.

24:36.840 --> 24:39.680
We headed off down
Molesworth Street.

24:39.800 --> 24:42.240
