24:45.160 --> 24:47.760
I still don't see why she'dmarry someone that much older.

24:47.880 --> 24:49.320
He's a prince.

24:49.440 --> 24:52.160
Wouldn't you marry a prince?

24:52.280 --> 24:53.360
Is Phineas all right?

24:53.480 --> 24:54.760
Yes.

24:54.880 --> 24:55.640
No.

24:55.760 --> 24:56.560
Who knows?

24:56.680 --> 24:58.080
I need some fresh air.

24:58.200 --> 24:59.360
I might join you.

24:59.480 --> 25:00.880
