25:01.000 --> 25:03.200
I know how they go.

25:03.320 --> 25:05.080
NEWSCASTER [ON TV]:
I, Diana Frances.

25:05.200 --> 25:06.480
I, Diana Frances.

25:06.600 --> 25:08.880
She's only 20 years old.

25:09.000 --> 25:11.560
Like a lamb to the slaughter.

25:11.680 --> 25:13.920
Imagine marrying
into that family.

25:14.040 --> 25:16.120
Queen Mum seems
like a good sort.

25:16.240 --> 25:18.360
And there's corgis.

25:18.480 --> 25:19.520
I've never been much on dogs.

25:23.920 --> 25:24.880
I've met someone.

25:27.760 --> 25:29.720
You're always meeting someone.

25:29.840 --> 25:32.280
This is a "someone" someone.

25:37.560 --> 25:39.280
What's his name?

25:39.400 --> 25:41.000
Steve.

25:41.120 --> 25:43.240
We met at this
restaurant in town.

25:43.360 --> 25:47.360
I was there with a
lady, but he still knew.

25:47.480 --> 25:48.920
Tracked me down in the bogs.

25:49.040 --> 25:51.600
Sounds romantic.

25:51.720 --> 25:52.760
I took him home.

25:52.880 --> 25:53.960
We've been inseparable
ever since.

25:56.680 --> 25:58.320
So he's the dollybird
you've been jetting

25:58.440 --> 26:00.120
off to Sydney with, then?

26:00.240 --> 26:02.240
There's a lot we can doover there we can't do here.

26:02.360 --> 26:03.160
I don't need to know.

26:05.840 --> 26:08.280
Thing is, Steve's amazing.

26:10.960 --> 26:12.560
He's so upfront about who he is.

26:12.680 --> 26:13.440
Doesn't care who knows.

26:17.120 --> 26:19.280
And I can be open with
him about who I am.

26:19.400 --> 26:21.800
How open?

26:21.920 --> 26:25.520
He knows what I do when I'mnot working behind a counter.

26:25.640 --> 26:27.600
Is that wise?

26:27.720 --> 26:32.120
Rita, the one thing gay peopleare good at is keeping secrets.

26:32.240 --> 26:33.040
And dancing.

26:38.560 --> 26:40.880
Well, you know
what you're doing,

26:41.000 --> 26:44.080
and as long as it
makes you happy.

26:44.200 --> 26:46.240
It does.

26:46.360 --> 26:48.400
"He said unhappily."

