People used to tease
me about my accent.

27:15.160 --> 27:16.760
What accent?

27:16.880 --> 27:20.480
Meine Muttersprache
ist Deutsch.

27:20.600 --> 27:22.440
German?

27:22.560 --> 27:24.400
Yeah.

27:24.520 --> 27:28.000
My family immigrated
here after the war.

27:33.200 --> 27:34.760
You really wanna know?

27:34.880 --> 27:37.240
